{"id":53550,"type":1,"name":"KAPPEI","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/85/6b/53550_tQKRP.jpg","summary":"　　為了在1999年7月的世界末日來臨時拯救人類的危機，一群男人從出生的時候，就在島上鍛鍊「無戒殺風拳」！但是到了2011年，世界末日還沒有來臨，他們的師父只好下令他們解散。於是這群只學過戰鬥的壯漢，就來到了2011年的日本。其中之一的勝平來到了東京，看在他的眼中，一切都是非常新鮮的。而且勝平居然還對一位叫做山瀨春的女大學生一見鍾情，可是完全沒有任何常識的這個末日戰士，根本不知道該怎麼做……而且他的師父除了拳法之外，居然只教了一些亂七八糟又詭異的常識……","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>末日救世主KAPPEI</li><li><span>册数: </span>6</li><li><span>话数: </span>59</li><li><span>作者: </span><a href=\"/person/3533\">若杉公徳</a></li><li><span>出版社: </span><a href=\"/person/588\">白泉社</a>、<a href=\"/person/7613\">玉皇朝</a>、<a href=\"/person/7033\">東立出版社</a></li><li><span>连载杂志: </span><a href=\"/person/7660\">ヤングアニマル</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>戇救世主</li><li><span>开始: </span>2011-05-27(2011年11号)</li><li><span>结束: </span>2014-08-22(2014年17号)</li>","collection":{"wish":1,"collect":1},"tags":[{"name":"漫画系列","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":3533,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/c7/93/3533_prsn_MtUzD.jpg","name":"若杉公德","desc":"作者"},{"id":7033,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/fd/24/7033_prsn_J3N83.jpg","name":"东立出版社","desc":"出版社"},{"id":588,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/2c/2a/588_prsn_0Fa4a.jpg","name":"白泉社","desc":"出版社"},{"id":7613,"image":"","name":"玉皇朝","desc":"出版社"},{"id":7660,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/e6/e2/7660_prsn_N8C2J.jpg","name":"ヤングアニマル","desc":"连载杂志"}],"comic":[{"id":53548,"name":"KAPPEI (1)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/35/ae/53548_jp.jpg"},{"id":52468,"name":"KAPPEI (2)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/84/71/52468_jp.jpg"},{"id":53549,"name":"KAPPEI (3)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/37/2f/53549_jp.jpg"},{"id":79274,"name":"KAPPEI (4)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/83/fc/79274_jp.jpg"},{"id":107077,"name":"KAPPEI (5)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/88/aa/107077_jp.jpg"},{"id":163714,"name":"KAPPEI (6)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/9e/31/163714_jp.jpg"}]}